00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:29,510
I can't marry them both into your family!

873
00:38:29,510 --> 00:38:31,070
Isn't that how it should be?

874
00:38:31,190 --> 00:38:32,800
That's forced marriage!

875
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:34,130
You're the Chancellor.

876
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:36,520
Shouldn't you help me with my concerns?

877
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,230
And also,

878
00:38:39,590 --> 00:38:41,030
why are you glaring at me?

879
00:38:41,030 --> 00:38:42,510
You also yelled at me.

880
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,930
Are you trying to offend your emperor?

881
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:46,360
I wouldn't dare.

882
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:50,110
I apologize.

883
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:57,560
You placed your piece there?

884
00:38:57,800 --> 00:38:59,170
No take-backs.

885
00:38:59,730 --> 00:39:01,120
I win.

886
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,360
You're terrible at this.

887
00:39:17,160 --> 00:39:18,840
This tastes really good.

888
00:39:23,070 --> 00:39:23,590
Father.

889
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,280
Don't you think you owe me

890
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,960
an explanation for what happened today?

891
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,670
Yesterday, you told me
why you didn't return to the capital,

892
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:29,400
and I understand that.

893
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:31,030
But how could you pretend
to have superpowers

894
00:39:31,030 --> 00:39:33,090
and live off trickery in the village?

895
00:39:34,520 --> 00:39:36,070
Watch your language, young man.

896
00:39:36,070 --> 00:39:37,070
Don't be so judgy.

897
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,080
Let me ask you—

898
00:39:39,670 --> 00:39:41,860
did the villagers dig up real ginseng?

899
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:44,760
And was that ginseng
already in the ground?

900
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,710
Lying about things that don't exist—

901
00:39:47,710 --> 00:39:48,670
that's a scam.

902
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:51,510
But I'm seriously

903
00:39:51,550 --> 00:39:53,400
helping the villagers get rich.

904
00:39:56,280 --> 00:39:56,840
But

905
00:39:57,630 --> 00:39:59,890
how did you know there was ginseng there?

906
00:40:00,060 --> 00:40:02,350
With a feather fan in hand

907
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:03,590
and a quick divination,

908
00:40:03,590 --> 00:40:04,870
I reveal the future…

909
00:40:05,480 --> 00:40:07,010
with the power of prophecy.

910
00:40:09,590 --> 00:40:11,230
If you really had the power of prophecy,

911
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:13,630
how would we have lost
the Pingrong Battle?

912
00:40:14,450 --> 00:40:15,510
Hey,

913
00:40:15,590 --> 00:40:17,800
do you have to keep bringing up
the Pingrong Battle?

914
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:19,110
It's been so long.

915
00:40:19,550 --> 00:40:20,810
It's time you let it go.

916
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:22,480
Let it go?

917
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:25,030
Father,

918
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:26,380
you've changed.

919
00:40:26,380 --> 00:40:28,030
The man you used to be
would never have let go of

920
00:40:28,030 --> 00:40:29,800
the 20,000 Qianyu soldiers we lost,

921
00:40:29,800 --> 00:40:32,730
nor would he believe in
such supernatural nonsense.

922
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:48,110
Son,

923
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,330
have you ever heard that

924
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,820
people can awaken certain gifts

925
00:40:51,820 --> 00:40:53,290
on the brink of death?

926
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:56,230
Take me, for example.

927
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:58,800
I awakened the gift of prophecy.

928
00:40:59,110 --> 00:41:00,280
If it hadn't been for saving you,

929
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,550
why would I have come here in advance,

930
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:02,880
befriended the villagers,

931
00:41:02,880 --> 00:41:05,190
and helped you out during your escape?

932
00:41:09,570 --> 00:41:10,890
So you knew in advance

933
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,480
that I'd flee here?

934
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:13,230
Yes.

935
00:41:14,070 --> 00:41:15,590
Not just that. I also know

936
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,710
you were rejected by the Song family,

937
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:19,640
that Song Yimeng fell for Nan Heng,

938
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:21,230
that His Majesty no longer trusts you,

939
00:41:21,230 --> 00:41:23,400
and that Nan Rui
has given up on the throne.

940
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,800
Now you're isolated,

941
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,190
and you feel like no one in this world

942
00:41:26,190 --> 00:41:27,730
can understand what you're going through.

943
00:41:27,730 --> 00:41:28,440
Am I right?

944
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,730
You really do know everything?

945
00:41:34,370 --> 00:41:36,030
You've been watching over me
this whole time?

946
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:37,000
Of course I have.

947
00:41:37,510 --> 00:41:38,920
You're my son.

948
00:41:39,670 --> 00:41:41,150
Now that we've reunited,

949
00:41:41,150 --> 00:41:42,440
you're not alone anymore.

950
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,590
As for the assassination,

951
00:41:43,590 --> 00:41:46,440
I sent Physician Zhao
ahead of time to save Nan Heng

952
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:48,570
so they'd spare you from punishment.

953
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:49,590
Also,

954
00:41:49,740 --> 00:41:51,490
I sent letters to Rong Hua

955
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:52,850
and Nan Rui yesterday.

956
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:54,070
From now on,

957
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,440
you'll have nothing to worry about.

958
00:41:58,590 --> 00:42:00,920
Father, you've really done so much for me.

959
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:04,840
I'm sorry.

960
00:42:05,880 --> 00:42:06,670
I failed to carry out

961
00:42:06,670 --> 00:42:09,200
the responsibilities
you entrusted me with.

962
00:42:09,590 --> 00:42:11,190
I've let you down.

963
00:42:13,550 --> 00:42:14,960
As long as you trust me,

964
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:16,280
nothing else matters.

965
00:42:18,590 --> 00:42:19,440
Guihong,

966
00:42:19,510 --> 00:42:22,170
His Majesty seems
to have turned his back on you,

967
00:42:22,410 --> 00:42:24,070
but once something happens to him,

968
00:42:24,070 --> 00:42:25,300
that will be our chance

969
00:42:25,300 --> 00:42:27,200
to make a comeback.

970
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:31,280
Something will happen to His Majesty?

971
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,070
Father,

972
00:42:32,390 --> 00:42:34,130
do you know something?

973
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,730
Some secrets cannot be revealed.

974
00:42:37,730 --> 00:42:38,630
Son,

975
00:42:39,100 --> 00:42:40,700
just wait for the good news.

